fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.annotations

Annotation Type ModelExportedVariable


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Repeatable(value=ModelExportedVariables.class)
 @Inherited
 @Documented
public @interface ModelExportedVariable
    The annotation ModelExportedVariable is used to declare variables that are exported by HIOA type of DEVS atomic models.

    Description

    The annotation must be put on HIOA atomic model classes that export variables. It can be repeated to cater for multiple exported variables.

    TODO: add treatment in library code.

    Black-box Invariant

     invariant       name() != null && !name().isEmpty()
 invariant       type() != null
